data.meta_description: From the Bloomsburg, PA Press-Enterprise October 26, 2022.  Harry Summy Hal Keller III, 87, passed away on Monday, October 24, 2022, surrounded by family. He was a renaissance man, loving the classics, international finance, literature and coastal Maine. He was born on December 30, 1934, the oldest child of Bernice and...
